{"tid":974313,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(無圖 )究竟點樣為之靚？","createTime":"2019-01-08T18:57:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-09T03:23:08.000Z","uid":136190,"like":56,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"05c1319aa49978086d8ade47342471da5536fd74","tid":974313,"uid":136190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T18:57:22.000Z","msg":"琴日同朋友傾開呢個話題<br />\n好自然講到到身邊嘅朋友<br />\n我見大家都好似慣性討論一個人化妝後嘅樣<br />\n而唔係討論先天嘅輪廓 <br />\n見咁嘅狀況我都廢事再傾 以免引起罵戰<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想問下大家討論一個人靚唔靚嘅時候睇妝前定妝後<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 妝前=純天然<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 妝後= 化妝/有微整/有紋眉個啲/植眼睫毛"},{"pid":"1f2c38d5b4dff70bf1e835ea34d1cc05a3762f60","tid":974313,"uid":50328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T18:58:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"05fef0c469a9a6d4cca21c413988729c1b9d2e36","tid":974313,"uid":136190,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f2c38d5b4dff70bf1e835ea34d1cc05a3762f60","tid":974313,"uid":50328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T18:58:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T19:00:13.000Z","msg":"唔係好明你講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a81f01b4eeafe2fb1b4baead045c7d237d40468","tid":974313,"uid":50328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T19:02:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"efb0373d344dc69eca2b923c38c268ad9cb8b62b","tid":974313,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T19:03:14.000Z","msg":"好多人整完好靚"},{"pid":"8ac9022708ddf8cef9d0961ea9600d37b8032a80","tid":974313,"uid":136190,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a81f01b4eeafe2fb1b4baead045c7d237d40468","tid":974313,"uid":50328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"05fef0c469a9a6d4cca21c413988729c1b9d2e36","tid":974313,"uid"